review_blob: To be honest this long lost IPA was far greater than Tallgrass's current Ethos. If only they would bring this awesome beer back!!

This is my all time favorite beer!! This complex porter has incredible flavor and is very drinkable! If you are ever in the Little Apple stop by the brewery for a good 'ol craft brewer tour. Great time!!
This beer resembles it big brother with a little less sweetness. Definitely worth the price for a tasty pint of imperial IPA. I buy these 4 packs of 16oz cans at least once a month.
Love Child is an overall pleasing experience. This great sour just goes to show what Boulevard is capable of
